text: Royal Mint can refer to any number of mints with a royal patronage, mints that have a Royal prefix include: *Royal Mint (United Kingdom) *Royal Australian Mint (Australia) *Royal Belgian Mint (Belgium) *Royal Canadian Mint (Canada) *Royal Danish Mint (Denmark) *Royal Dutch Mint (Netherlands) *Royal Hungarian State Mint, now known as the Hungarian Mint *Royal Mint of Malaysia (Malaysia) *Royal Mint (Spain) *Royal Norwegian Mint (Norway) *Royal Thai Mint (Thailand)
title: Royal Mint (disambiguation)
